{"text_id":253065,"tokens":["Atomic"," shells"," are"," the"," region"," around"," the"," nucleus"," of"," an"," atom"," where"," an"," electron"," is"," likely"," to"," be"," found","."," Each"," shell"," has"," a"," specific"," energy"," level"," and"," can"," hold"," a"," certain"," maximum"," number"," of"," electrons","."," The"," maximum"," number"," of"," electrons"," an"," atomic"," shell"," can"," hold"," is"," ","1","8"," due"," to"," the"," principles"," of"," quantum"," mechanics"," and"," the"," configuration"," of"," the"," atomic"," orbitals","."," ","\n\n","The"," first"," shell",","," also"," known"," as"," the"," ","1","s"," shell",","," can"," hold"," a"," maximum"," of"," two"," electrons","."," This"," is"," because"," the"," electrons"," in"," this"," shell"," are"," in"," the"," s"," orbital",","," which"," is"," a"," spher","ically"," symmetrical"," region"," around"," the"," nucleus","."," The"," second"," shell",","," or"," ","2","s"," and"," ","2","p"," shells",","," can"," hold"," a"," maximum"," of"," eight"," electrons","."," This"," is"," because"," the"," electrons"," in"," this"," shell"," are"," in"," the"," p"," orbitals",","," which"," are"," dumbbell","-","shaped"," and"," can"," point"," in"," different"," directions","."," The"," third"," shell",","," or"," ","3","s",","," ","3","p",","," and"," ","3","d"," shells",","," can"," hold"," a"," maximum"," of"," ","1","8"," electrons","."," This"," is"," because"," the"," electrons"," in"," this"," shell"," are"," in"," the"," d"," orbitals",","," which"," are"," more"," complex"," and"," can"," be"," oriented"," in"," multiple"," ways","."," The"," d"," orbitals"," can"," accommodate"," more"," electrons"," because"," of"," their"," increased"," complexity"," and"," flexibility","."," ","\n\n","In"," addition",","," the"," energy"," levels"," of"," the"," electrons"," in"," the"," outermost"," shell",","," also"," known"," as"," the"," valence"," shell",","," play"," a"," crucial",